column16: Description
Frequented Disneyland with parents

Sexually abused by uncle and grandfather. Abuse by uncle started around ~2 and was ongoing. I was not around him much though. Abuse by grandfather started around ~5 and was ongoing. I was around him more.
Trip to drive-in with aunt and cousins to see Grease in convertible cadillac.
Terrible domestic violence incident - mother injured and sent to hospital.
Evicted from home in CityA - had to abruptly move and leave personal belongings behind.
Attempted attack on dad and uncle due to dad and uncle not completing "job" as part of organized crime. Family members barricaded themselves in restaurant.
Had to flee house in the middle of the night to get away from mafia and get out of Florida. Could see flames in out side of mirror - not sure if it was in the driveway or part of the house.
Maternal grandmother died
Ongoing domestic violence - Angry outbursts and spankings from dad. Cocaine and meth use by dad.
Won a dance competition
Birth of Aunt's twins
Snow-skiing and beach vacations
Vacation to California beach and Magic Mountain with family
Lots of fun social happenings during this time period
Father nearly died due to complications from major surgery. He was told he would never walk again so we were trying to prepare ourselves for that and he was very abuse verbally and using cocaine
First homecoming and first prom
Ongoing domestic violence at home. Started physically fighting with dad.
Parents forced me to have an abortion. Had an older boyfriend (18 y/o) who was very angry and physically abused me for getting the abortion. Painful and awful and I thought I was going to hell.
Vacation to CityC with friends
Close friends and boyfriend of my best friend committed armed robbery and killed someone. My best friend and I hid them out for a couple of days until the police found them.
Moved to Oklahoma - it was against my will and it felt like the end of the world.
Multiple good vacations
Death of Aunt
Mother left family and went to live with her family in California

Apprehended for interstate drug trafficking. My codependent boyfriend was nearly killed by police during the incident. Was incarcerated (held without bond) for 11 months. Co-dependent boyfriend was sentenced to 15 years.
Birth of first 2 children (1995/1998)
Boyfriend shot me up with meth IV against my will after I had been clean for multiple years. Led to full blown addiction for next couple of years.
Boyfriend stabbed me. He kidnapped me. He shot a gun at me. He tried to run me and my children over with a vehicle. He physically and sexually abused me multiple times.
Son Born

My father was arrested and sent to prison for 15 years for a crime he did not commit - manufacturing methamphetamine. He took a plea deal and plead guilty to avoid a jury trial where he probably would have received a life sentence.
Granddaughter born
Accepted in to WIR
Mother's home burned down. She and her husband and my granddaughter barely escaped but were not injured. All the pets were lost.
Re-unified with all children - all children living in one home.
Brother was incarcerated and then escaped prison and was on the run for a couple of weeks.
Daughter overdosed on opiates (heroin). The medics could not find a pulse and she was not breathing - it felt like time froze. She was able to be revived.
Moved in to a beautiful home in a beautiful neighborhood
Dad almost died from COVID. Hospitalized and on vent. Long lasting effects.
Daughter moved home from KY
Bought a boat
